'''Air New Zealand''' is the national airline and flag carrier of [[New Zealand]] based in Auckland. 

It has promoted the films by Sir [[Peter Jackson]], such as the "Hobbit Jet", and also, with cooperation with Jackson and [[Weta Workshop]], released several cross-promotion Middle-earth inspired videos. 

The videos feature [[Tolkien]] characters such as [[Gandalf]] and [[Gwaihir]], [[Orcs]], [[Hobbits]] and [[Elves]] or the [[One Ring]]. Jackson, [[Dean O'Gorman]], [[Sylvester McCoy]] and [[Elijah Wood]] make cameos.
